content: I don't have an accurate answer to this question because the time taken to see improvement in vocal range and control can vary widely depending on numerous factors such as the current vocal range and control, age, natural ability, and consistent practicing of these methods. however, it's essential to remember that vocal improvement is a gradual process and requires consistent effort, patience, and practice over an extended period. in general, you can expect to see some improvement in your vocal range and control within a few weeks or months of practicing these methods regularly.
